an penyakit (kebutuhan akan biosecurity, karantina, pengamatan, penelitian tentang penyebab penyakit, dan penyakit itu sendiri) \uf0b7 Risiko bencana yang berdampak pada program ex situ (bencana alam maupun yang disebabkan oleh manusia seperti kebakaran, pergolakan", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "811eb94a-c17f-4b26-ab63-210986dc5960": {"__data__": {"id_": "811eb94a-c17f-4b26-ab63-210986dc5960", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/komisi-penyelamatan-spesies-iucn-panduan-manajemen-ex-situ-untuk", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Komisi Penyelamatan Spesies IUCN panduan manajemen ex situ untuk konservasi spesies", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/komisi-penyelamatan-spesies-iucn-panduan-manajemen-ex-situ-untuk", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "c4e34525a1a4e98e2e06d54e8341d7a4807ee270e68c1aec102e41eb5e61a374"}, "3": {"node_id": "20b1f990-58c8-403b-8b72-d21a9dcd23b6", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/komisi-penyelamatan-spesies-iucn-panduan-manajemen-ex-situ-untuk", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "3fea77034acec6e19363f8645d0640c98f093f7d3f1e531562011cd82c30e524"}}, "hash": "baaa034b3d0b77c8ef2fc5aee8ba48a6bc66e3bd4421d212225ff37b203c7faf", "text": "masyarakat, dan lain-lain); dan \uf0b7 Pendanaa